#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 62. Mahāpaññāsutta → mahā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.62:0.3"
msgid "62. Mahāpaññāsutta"
msgstr "62. Great Wisdom"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.412"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.62:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahāpaññatāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr "“Mendicants, when four things are developed and cultivated they lead to great wisdom."

msgctxt "sn55.62:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.62:1.3"
msgid "Sappurisasaṃsevo, saddhammassavanaṃ, yonisomanasikāro, dhammānudhammappaṭipatti—"
msgstr "Associating with good people, listening to the true teaching, proper attention, and practicing in line with the teaching."

msgctxt "sn55.62:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahāpaññatāya saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr "When these four things are developed and cultivated they lead to great wisdom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.62:1.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
